ames Terry]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Commanding General of the [[10th Mountain Division (United States)|10th Mountain Division]]|years=2011\u20132012}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Stephen J. Townsend|Stephen Townsend]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Donald M. Campbell, Jr.|Donald Campbell]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Commanding General of [[III Corps (United States)|III Corps]]|years=2012\u20132014}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Sean MacFarland]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[James L. Terry|James Terry]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Commanding General of [[International Security Assistance Force|ISAF-Joint Command]]|years=2013\u20132014}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Joseph Anderson (U.S. Army general)|Joseph Anderson]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Daniel B. Allyn|Daniel Allyn]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Commanding General of [[United States Army Forces Command]]|years=2014\u20132015}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Robert B. Abrams]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Raymond T. Odierno]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Chief of Staff of the United States Army]]|years=2015\u20132019}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[James C. McConville]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Joseph Dunford]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff]]|years=2019\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc}}\n|-\n{{s-prec|us}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Barbara Barrett]]|as=[[Secretary of the Air Force]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[United States order of precedence|Order of Precedence of the United States]]<br />''{{small|as Chair of the Joint Chiefs of Staff}}''|years=}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Jerome Powell]]|as=Chair of the Federal Reserve}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Current JCS members}}\n{{CJCS}}\n{{US Army Chiefs of Staff}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Milley, Mark A.}}\n[[Category:1958 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American army personnel of the Iraq War]]\n[[Category:Belmont Hill School alumni]]\n[[Category:School of International and Public Affairs, Columbia University alumni]]\n[[Category:Members of the United States Army Special Forces]]\n[[Category:Military personnel from Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Naval War College alumni]]\n[[Category:People from Winchester, Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Princeton Tigers men's ice hockey players]]\n[[Category:Princeton University alumni]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Legion of Merit]]\n[[Category:United States Army generals]]\n[[Category:Chairmen of the Joint Chiefs of Staff]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Meritorious Service Medal (United States)]]\n", "name_user": "Abraham, B.S.", "label": "safe", "comment": "tidy", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mark_A._Milley"}
